snippet.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles (2014) VS Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles (1990) : Movie Feuds ep99

localized.description:
Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles clashes against the 90's original. Producer Michael Bay and director Jonathan Liebesman give us the first live-action Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles film since the 1990's. There was an animated flick in the early 2000's but we don't talk about TMNT. So put down your skateboards, grab a slice of pizza and join Adam Olinger and Jessica Chobot as they feud heroes in a half-shell on Movie Feuds.
